Class AbstractMappingHTTPResponseHandler<T>

java.lang.Object

          org.fax4j.spi.http.AbstractMappingHTTPResponseHandler<T>
Type Parameters:
T - The specific data object
All Implemented Interfaces:
ConfigurationHolder, Initializable, ProviderImplementation, Service, HTTPResponseHandler
Direct Known Subclasses:
JSONHTTPResponseHandler, XMLHTTPResponseHandler
public abstract class AbstractMappingHTTPResponseHandler<T>
extends AbstractHTTPResponseHandler

This class provides an abstract mapping based implementation of the HTTP response handler interface.
This class expects to get a data object and will update the fax job as needed.
This class only supports extracting the fax job ID and fax job status from the response object, or in case of errors, extract the error message.

Since:
0.42.8
Version:

Author:
Sagie Gur-Ari
